ing his £45million deadline-day move from Atletico Madrid – ended in disappointment as Jamie Vardy sealed all three points for Leicester at the Emirates. But the 27-year-old shone as the Gunners travelled to Old Trafford last weekend and his statement performance earned rave reviews from supporters, pundits and team-mates alike. Aubameyang, who scored the only goal of the game from the penalty spot in the 69th minute, discussed the victory in the club’s matchday programme and praised Partey for the seamless transition he’s made into the team. Vanguard Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang has agreed personal terms with Arsenal but the Gunners are yet to strike a deal with Borussia Dormtund for the Gabon international, reports claim. January 23, 2018 In "Sports" Arsenal top striker Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang, has urged his teammates to post another top class performance when they clash with Manchester United on Wednesday at Old Traford. December 3, 2018 In "Sports" Manchester City completed the signing of Aymeric Laporte on Tuesday as Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang reportedly arrived at Arsenal's training ground to finalise his transfer from Borussia Dortmund, with clubs scrambling to beat Wednesday's deadline. January 30, 2018 In "Sports"